PUBLIC DOMAIN

This database compilation is released into the public domain. You may
copy, modify, distribute, and use it for any purpose, without restriction
or attribution.

The vast majority of texts included here are from public domain
translations of ancient works. It is possible that a small number of
quotes may originate from copyrighted translations. If you are the
copyright holder of any such translation and would like it removed,
please open an issue on this repository.
